sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AuthCtrl as Authentication Controller
    participant MTLSCtrl as mTLS Controller
    participant NPCtrl as NetworkPolicy Controller
    participant RCCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: RayCluster Provisioning (RHOAI Auth)

        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>MutWH: Admission Review<br/>TLS (cert-manager)
        MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Set odh.ray.io/secure-trusted-network=true<br/>Disable enableIngress
        K8sAPI->>ValWH: Validation Review<br/>TLS (cert-manager)
        ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Validated (name format + unique groups)

        par Security Controllers (parallel)
            K8sAPI->>AuthCtrl: RayCluster event
            AuthCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute + ReferenceGrant<br/>in platform namespace
            AuthCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount + ConfigMap
            AuthCtrl->>K8sAPI: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar

            K8sAPI->>MTLSCtrl: RayCluster event
            MTLSCtrl->>CertMgr: Create Issuer (SelfSigned→CA chain)
            MTLSCtrl->>CertMgr: Create Certificate (head + worker)
            CertMgr-->>MTLSCtrl: TLS secrets provisioned<br/>(90-day, renew at 75 days)

            K8sAPI->>NPCtrl: RayCluster event
            NPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (head)<br/>Allow: intra-cluster, ingress NS, monitoring NS
            NPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (workers)<br/>Allow: intra-cluster only
        end

        K8sAPI->>RCCtrl: RayCluster event (reconcile)
        RCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + Services
        RCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods
        RCCtrl-->>K8sAPI: Set status: AuthenticationReady
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1 (cont): Authenticated Dashboard Access

        User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}/*<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: OIDC Bearer Token
        Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP TLS
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Auth result
        KRBP->>Dashboard: Forward (authenticated)<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP (localhost)
        Dashboard-->>KRBP: Response
        KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: JSON/HTML Response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 2: RayJob Submission (K8sJobMode)

        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>RCCtrl: RayJob controller creates RayCluster
        RCCtrl-->>K8sAPI: RayCluster Ready
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Create batch/Job (submitter pod)
        K8sAPI->>Dashboard: Submitter: POST job<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP (or mTLS)
        Dashboard-->>K8sAPI: Job ID
        loop Status polling (until complete)
            K8sAPI->>Dashboard: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP
            Dashboard-->>K8sAPI: Job status
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Workers: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Upgrade

        User->>K8sAPI: PUT RayService CR (updated spec)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>RCCtrl: Create pending RayCluster
        RCCtrl-->>K8sAPI: Pending cluster Ready
        K8sAPI->>Dashboard: PUT /api/serve/applications<br/>Deploy serve config<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP
        Dashboard-->>K8sAPI: Deployment accepted
        loop Health checks
            K8sAPI->>HeadPod: GET proxy health<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
            HeadPod-->>K8sAPI: Health status
        end
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Switch Service selectors<br/>(active → pending)
        Note over K8sAPI: 60s grace period
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Delete old RayCluster
    end
